name: Ame-chan (Needy Streamer Overload) holding dutch flag
description:
The main protagonist's full body appearance from the game "Needy Streamer Overload" (also known as "Needy Girl Overdose").

Needy Streamer Overload is a 2022 denpa-themed adventure visual novel created by Japanese developer Xemono and published by WSS Playground for macOS, Microsoft Windows, and Nintendo Switch.

Ame-chan is her true identity off-camera; by night she streams as "OMGkawaiiAngel" (or "kAngel" for short).
